243
00:16:56,468 --> 00:16:57,958
Captain...

244
00:16:58,671 --> 00:17:01,231
...this is a chance for you
to make a name for yourself.

245
00:17:01,407 --> 00:17:03,136
Yes, sir, I feel that I personally...

246
00:17:03,309 --> 00:17:06,642
...have delayed victory at least a year,
and I want to vindicate myself.

247
00:17:06,812 --> 00:17:08,609
That's the kind of talk I like to hear.

248
00:17:08,781 --> 00:17:10,840
- Thank you.
- Well, I won't detain you then.

249
00:17:11,016 --> 00:17:12,984
- Yes, sir.
- My only order to you is...

250
00:17:13,152 --> 00:17:15,052
...put that village on the map.

251
00:17:15,454 --> 00:17:16,443
Yes, sir.

252
00:17:16,622 --> 00:17:19,022
Send me a bimonthly progress report
in triplicate.

253
00:17:19,191 --> 00:17:21,159
- Yes, sir.
- Don't duplicate your work.

254
00:17:21,327 --> 00:17:22,555
No, sir. No, sir.

255
00:17:22,728 --> 00:17:26,164
And remember that the eyes of Washington
are on our occupation teams...

256
00:17:26,332 --> 00:17:28,459
...and the eyes of the world
are on Washington.

257
00:17:28,634 --> 00:17:31,626
- Yes, sir. I'll keep the eyes in mind, sir.
