275
00:18:31,563 --> 00:18:35,226
Well, all right. You see...
She's tied on all right, I guess, huh?

276
00:18:35,401 --> 00:18:37,369
- So I guess we can take her.
- Sure.

277
00:18:37,536 --> 00:18:42,599
