284
00:19:02,695 --> 00:19:05,960
No, no, can't go yet.
Old lady daughter not here, boss.

285
00:19:06,131 --> 00:19:08,656
Wait a minute,
maybe I didn't hear you right. You say...

286
00:19:08,834 --> 00:19:10,927
