325
00:21:13,892 --> 00:21:16,952
- Oh, no, no, please.
- Everyone here, boss.

326
00:21:17,129 --> 00:21:20,326
- Goat unmarried lady goat. No children.
- No, you'll have to get down.

327
00:21:20,499 --> 00:21:23,127
You'll never get it
off the ground, captain.

328
00:21:24,303 --> 00:21:26,965
- Sakini, come on, we gotta get started.
- You get in, boss.

329
00:21:27,139 --> 00:21:30,870
And no one else going, boss.
No one else is going.

330
00:21:33,612 --> 00:21:35,807
- Wait a minute.
- Hey, you got another customer.

331
00:21:35,981 --> 00:21:38,973
- Hey, wait a minute.
- Oh, no.

332
00:21:39,151 --> 00:21:41,449
- Sakini! Wait. Please wait.
- What?

333
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:43,918
Now, who in the blazes is he?

334
00:21:44,089 --> 00:21:47,547
Who in the blazes is he, boss?
Never see before.

335
00:21:47,726 --> 00:21:51,059
Ask him what he's doing sitting here,
please.

336
00:21:55,067 --> 00:21:57,262
He say he see people
going on a trip, boss.

337
00:21:57,436 --> 00:21:59,597
- He think he like to go along too.
- No, please...

338
00:21:59,771 --> 00:22:04,731
He does? Well, you tell him for me
that he's gotta get off right now.

339
00:22:04,910 --> 00:22:06,537
Come on.

340
00:22:07,980 --> 00:22:10,175
No, no. What?

341
00:22:10,349 --> 00:22:12,977
Oh, he say why you not take him, boss?

342
00:22:13,151 --> 00:22:14,482
- You take goat.
- Oh, no.

343
00:22:14,653 --> 00:22:16,780
He say maybe you think
he not as good as goat.

344
00:22:16,955 --> 00:22:21,415
Tell him for me, Sakini,
that the eyes of Washington are on...

345
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:25,154
The world is on Washington,
and the eyes of Washington are on me.

346
00:22:25,330 --> 00:22:28,163
Will you just... Folks, please,
I would love to take you.

347
00:22:28,333 --> 00:22:29,664
Folks, if this was my jeep...

348
00:22:29,835 --> 00:22:32,531
...or if this wasn't against regulations,
I'd be only too...

