350
00:22:34,373 --> 00:22:36,102
What do you think you're doing?

351
00:22:36,275 --> 00:22:40,075
Well, it's hard to explain, sir. No, just...

352
00:22:40,913 --> 00:22:42,642
What are they saying?

353
00:22:42,814 --> 00:22:46,079
They say tell fat old man to shut up
so we can get started.

354
00:22:52,224 --> 00:22:55,716
Which one of you men made that noise?

355
00:23:01,466 --> 00:23:05,334
Just a second. Where are you going?
Hey, Captain Fisby. Sakini.

356
00:23:05,504 --> 00:23:07,165
Come back here. You hear me?

357
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:39,160
No, just a minute please.
Just a minute. Which road?

358
00:23:44,009 --> 00:23:46,773
Just a minute please, just a minute.
What did she say?

359
00:23:46,945 --> 00:23:49,641
Old lady say, boss,
that she want to go to Awasi, boss...

360
00:23:49,815 --> 00:23:53,581
...because she got sister she not see
in 22 half years.

361
00:23:53,752 --> 00:23:56,346
We're on duty, Sakini,
we're not on a tour of the island.

362
00:23:56,521 --> 00:24:00,719
Now, would you please just ask her for me,
which is the road to Tobiki?

363
00:24:04,229 --> 00:24:05,457
- That way.
- This way?

364
00:24:05,631 --> 00:24:07,326
All right, that's all I asked you.

365
00:24:21,847 --> 00:24:24,611
All right. All right.

366
00:24:24,783 --> 00:24:28,742
- Well, so this is Tobiki.
- Tobiki, no. This Awasi, boss.

367
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:32,412
I distinctly asked this lady
to tell me the way to Tobiki.

368
00:24:32,591 --> 00:24:35,116
Well, old lady make mistake, boss.
Very sorry.

369
00:24:35,293 --> 00:24:38,956
- Well, you know, we can't go...
- Oh, sorry, boss, but she not very smart.

370
00:24:39,131 --> 00:24:40,723
Yeah.

371
00:24:51,843 --> 00:24:53,538
All right, which road?

372
00:24:53,712 --> 00:24:56,442
No, no, don't ask her. I don't trust her.

373
00:24:59,184 --> 00:25:03,518
- All right. What are they saying?
- Children want to go to Yatoda, boss.

374
00:25:03,789 --> 00:25:06,849
I suppose they've got some
cousins that they want to visit there.

375
00:25:07,025 --> 00:25:09,459
No, ocean at Yatoda, boss.

376
00:25:09,628 --> 00:25:10,890
Children never see ocean.

377
00:25:11,496 --> 00:25:14,590
Our orders are to proceed
directly to Tobiki.

378
00:25:14,766 --> 00:25:16,461
Now, which road?

379
00:25:18,470 --> 00:25:19,869
There.

380
00:25:20,839 --> 00:25:23,171
There. Over here, huh?

381
00:25:23,341 --> 00:25:25,172
All right.

382
00:25:43,962 --> 00:25:46,760
- Boss...
- No, don't tell me, this is Yatoda.

383
00:25:46,932 --> 00:25:49,696
- How you know, boss?
- Well, I recognize the ocean.

384
00:26:14,493 --> 00:26:17,621
Where is this? Whose uncle
or cousin lives here?

385
00:26:17,796 --> 00:26:19,320
This Tobiki, boss.

386
00:26:20,899 --> 00:26:22,526
- Sakini!
- I don't believe it.

387
00:26:22,701 --> 00:26:24,760
I don't believe it.

388
00:26:36,114 --> 00:26:37,342
Now, according to plan B...

389
00:26:37,516 --> 00:26:40,110
...my first job here is to
hold a public meeting, Sakini.

390
00:26:40,285 --> 00:26:42,845
You see, I want to make
certain that they understand...

391
00:26:43,021 --> 00:26:45,251
...that I come as their friend.
- Sure.

