396
00:26:57,068 --> 00:26:59,468
- Then take everything.
- No, no, no.

397
00:26:59,671 --> 00:27:02,799
No, you don't understand.
We don't come to take anything from them.

398
00:27:02,974 --> 00:27:04,908
We've come here
to give them something.

399
00:27:05,076 --> 00:27:07,203
That's all right, boss. We not mind.

400
00:27:07,379 --> 00:27:10,212
After eight centuries, we get used to it.

401
00:27:10,382 --> 00:27:11,849
Now when friends come...

402
00:27:12,017 --> 00:27:14,349
...we hide everything quick as dickens.

403
00:27:14,853 --> 00:27:18,789
So I'm go tell people
you make your speech, boss.

404
00:27:18,957 --> 00:27:22,017
So socks up, boss.

405
00:28:03,501 --> 00:28:05,264
Everyone here eager to meet you, boss.

406
00:28:05,437 --> 00:28:06,870
Might as well get started.

407
00:28:07,038 --> 00:28:08,403
- Citizens of...
- Up here, boss.

408
00:28:08,573 --> 00:28:10,063
- They'll see you.
- Thank you.

409
00:28:10,242 --> 00:28:12,642
Citizens of Tobiki...

410
00:28:18,116 --> 00:28:20,482
- Citizens of Tobiki village...
- Sorry, boss.

411
00:28:20,652 --> 00:28:23,621
- Can't begin lecture yet.
- What seems to be the trouble?

412
00:28:23,788 --> 00:28:26,052
- Not good manners, boss.
- Why?

413
00:28:26,224 --> 00:28:29,352
Because people bring you gifts.
You must accept gifts first.

414
00:28:29,527 --> 00:28:32,394
No, Sakini, wait a minute,
you got it all wrong.

415
00:28:32,564 --> 00:28:34,896
I'm here to bring gifts
from my government to them.

416
00:28:35,066 --> 00:28:37,933
No, very rude.
Make people feel poor, boss.

417
00:28:38,103 --> 00:28:40,037
I don't want to do that. Get up, Sakini.

418
00:28:40,238 --> 00:28:42,502
Tell them I'll accept gifts,
but in the name...

419
00:28:42,674 --> 00:28:45,575
...of the United States
occupation forces.

420
00:28:46,878 --> 00:28:48,175
All right?

421
00:28:50,849 --> 00:28:53,545
Here Mr. Hokaida, boss.
He give you very nice gift.

422
00:28:53,718 --> 00:28:56,084
Oh, thank you very, very much.
