Thank him for me.

429
00:29:11,403 --> 00:29:14,668
Tell him I'll keep
my eye open for a cricket.

430
00:29:14,839 --> 00:29:17,273
Yeah. What do you keep a
cricket in a cage for?

431
00:29:17,442 --> 00:29:20,275
So fortune smile on you, boss.
A cricket very good luck.

432
00:29:20,445 --> 00:29:22,970
- Oh, that's nice.
- Boss, here Mr. Omura.

433
00:29:23,148 --> 00:29:24,945
He give you chopstick.

434
00:29:27,018 --> 00:29:29,612
- What did he say?
- He say hope that only food...

435
00:29:29,788 --> 00:29:32,882
