436
00:29:33,058 --> 00:29:35,049
That's one of the
nicest things I've heard.

437
00:29:35,226 --> 00:29:38,195
- Boss, Mr. Seiko.
- Yes?

438
00:29:39,764 --> 00:29:41,231
Thank you.

439
00:29:44,836 --> 00:29:48,237
That's wooden sandal, boss,
very comfortable for tired feet.

440
00:29:48,406 --> 00:29:50,465
He say may you walk in prosperity.

441
00:29:50,642 --> 00:29:55,341
You tell him that I will walk in the
cool meadow of pleasant memories.

442
00:29:56,982 --> 00:30:01,043
- What's the matter? Is that all right?
- Oh, boss, that's very pretty, boss.

443
00:30:02,420 --> 00:30:05,651
Thank you. That's all right.
